        "path": [
          "api",
          "auth",
          "email",
          "verification-notification"
        ]
      },
      "description": "Resend a verification email for the authenticated central user.\n\n**Auth:** requires authenticated central session/token (`auth:central-api`).\n\n**Query params:** none\n\n**Request body validation:**\n- `reason`: sometimes|string|in:signup,update\n  - defaults to `signup` when omitted\n\n**Behavior:**\n- If user is already verified, returns `422 VALIDATION_ERROR`\n- Otherwise sends a new verification link and returns a success message\n- Endpoint is rate-limited (`throttle:auth.email_verification`)"
    },
